earlier in El Capitan with OS X,

01:02:56.206 --> 01:02:59.209 align:middle
we've taken the core frameworks
that we use for drawing

01:02:59.209 --> 01:03:01.711 align:middle
on the system, Core
Animation and Core Graphics,


WEBVTT
