on the system, Core
Animation and Core Graphics,

01:03:01.711 --> 01:03:02.912 align:middle
and we put them on top of Metal.

01:03:02.912 --> 01:03:04.914 align:middle
We are seeing great
acceleration,

01:03:04.914 --> 01:03:08.685 align:middle
1.6 times improvements in
animations and scrolling,

01:03:08.685 --> 01:03:11.621 align:middle
and a 50 percent reduction
in CPU usage for drawing.

01:03:11.621 --> 01:03:13.390 align:middle
It's really great.

01:03:13.390 --> 01:03:15.425 align:middle
With battery life, we focused

01:03:15.425 --> 01:03:19.162 align:middle
on real-world use cases
and optimized them.

01:03:19.162 --> 01:03:23.400 align:middle
And we are seeing an addition
of one hour of typical use

01:03:23.400 --> 01:03:26.102 align:middle
on a full charge on iPhone.

01:03:26.102 --> 01:03:30.507 align:middle
[Applause]

01:03:30.507 --> 01:03:32.776 align:middle
Now, we know that for a lot
of you if you are running low

01:03:32.776 --> 01:03:35.378 align:middle
