all over for switches

01:03:35.378 --> 01:03:37.213 align:middle
and turning off features
in the hope

01:03:37.213 --> 01:03:40.350 align:middle
of extending your battery
life a little bit further.

01:03:40.350 --> 01:03:43.319 align:middle
Well, now in iOS 9, we
give you a single switch

01:03:43.319 --> 01:03:46.356 align:middle
to enter what we call Low
Power mode, and it pulls levers

01:03:46.356 --> 01:03:48.892 align:middle
that you didn't even
know existed and is able

01:03:48.892 --> 01:03:53.463 align:middle
to extend battery life for
an additional three hours

01:03:53.463 --> 01:03:55.965 align:middle
of typical use on top
of that additional hour.

01:03:55.965 --> 01:03:57.133 align:middle
It's really great.

01:03:57.133 --> 01:04:02.939 align:middle
[Applause]


WEBVTT
