01:08:59.102 --> 01:09:04.607 align:middle
Now, we think Swift is the
next big programming language,

01:09:04.607 --> 01:09:07.076 align:middle
the one that we will
all be doing application

01:09:07.076 --> 01:09:11.913 align:middle
and systems programming
on for 20 years to come.

01:09:11.913 --> 01:09:17.520 align:middle
