everywhere and used by everyone,

01:09:17.520 --> 01:09:20.555 align:middle
and so we're going to be
doing something really big.

01:09:20.555 --> 01:09:25.461 align:middle
Today we are announcing that
Swift will be open source.

01:09:25.461 --> 01:09:34.537 align:middle
[Cheers and applause]

01:09:48.885 --> 01:09:51.854 align:middle
We will be rolling
out the compiler

01:09:51.854 --> 01:09:56.959 align:middle
and the standard libraries
for iOS, OS X, and Linux.

01:09:56.959 --> 01:10:02.598 align:middle
And it will all be out there
by the end of the year.


WEBVTT
X-TIMESTAMP-MAP=MPEGTS:181083,LOCAL:00:00:00.000

01:09:56.959 --> 01:10:02.598 align:middle
And it will all be out there
by the end of the year.

