01:17:19.068 --> 01:17:22.171 align:middle
and there's an incredible
generation of filmmakers

01:17:22.171 --> 01:17:24.106 align:middle
and storytellers to come.

01:17:33.516 --> 01:17:37.253 align:middle
&gt;&gt; Kids love technology,
and they love interacting

01:17:37.253 --> 01:17:40.890 align:middle
with the iPad and with apps.

01:17:40.890 --> 01:17:44.860 align:middle
That wonder and awe that gets
ignited is actually being

01:17:44.860 --> 01:17:48.030 align:middle
