Let's go through
some of the things

01:31:18.073 --> 01:31:20.241 align:middle
that will be possible
now in watchOS 2.

01:31:20.241 --> 01:31:21.643 align:middle
You can see how we did on this.

01:31:21.643 --> 01:31:24.079 align:middle
So one of the things we
heard was really wanted

01:31:24.079 --> 01:31:26.614 align:middle
to access the microphone
